City of St. Louis Boundary

A simple features data set containing a single polygon with the extent of the City of St. Louis's boundary.

data(stlBoundary)

Format

A simple feature with 1 rows and 6 variables:

LAYER

polygon description

AREA_SQMI

square mileage of city

Name

polygon name

Shape_Leng

length of polygon

Shape_Area

area of polygon

geometry

simple features geometry
